message: Even though this is a big step in the fight against the sex trade, some undercover officers who work with human trafficking victims said it won't stop criminals from selling sex online.

data.description: DELAWARE COUNTY, Ind. – A popular classified website has been shut down by the federal government and the founder has been arrested on multiple charges. data.title: Undercover deputies say shutdown of Backpage.com won’t stop human trafficking
